ntroller,PlayStation controller,PC gamepad\"/><meta name=\"creator\" content=\"GamepadTester Team\"/><meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow\"/><meta name=\"googlebot\" content=\"index, follow, max-video-preview:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-snippet:-1\"/><meta name=\"category\" content=\"technology\"/><link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://gamepadtester.live/privacy\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Professional Gamepad Tester &amp; Diagnostics\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Test your gamepad/controller with advanced diagnostics, compatibility checking, and troubleshooting guides.\"/><meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://gamepadtester.live\"/><meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"GamepadTester.live\"/><meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\"/><meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://gamepadtester.live/og-image.png\"/><meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"1200\"/><meta property=\"og:image:height\" content=\"630\"/><meta property=\"og:image:alt\" content=\"GamepadTester.live\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"Professional Gamepad Tester\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Test your gamepad with advanced diagnostics and compatibility checking.\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://gamepadtester.live/twitter-image.png\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.svg\"/><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"WebApplication\",\"name\":\"GamepadTester.live\",\"description\":\"Professional gamepad and controller testing platform with diagnostics\",\"url\":\"https://gamepadtester.live\",\"applicationCategory\":\"UtilityApplication\",\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"Offer\",\"price\":\"0\",\"priceCurrency\":\"USD\"}}</script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body><main class=\"min-h-screen bg-background flex flex-col font-sans\"><nav class=\"sticky top-0 z-50 transition-all duration-300 bg-background/80 backdrop-blur border-b border-border/50\"><div class=\"container-custom\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center h-16\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xl font-bold text-primary hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity\" href=\"/\"><svg class=\"inline-block\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#ff7a00\" stroke-width=\"2.2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle\"><rect x=\"2\" y=\"6\" width=\"20\" height=\"12\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"rgba(255, 122, 0, 0.12)\"></rect><path d=\"M6 12h4M8 10v4\" stroke=\"#ff7a00\" stroke-width=\"2.2\"></path><circle cx=\"16\" cy=\"10\" r=\"1\" fill=\"#ff7a00\" stroke=\"none\"></circle><circle cx=\"18\" cy=\"12\" r=\"1\" fill=\"#ff7a00\" stroke=\"none\"></circle><circle cx=\"16\" cy=\"14\" r=\"1\" fill=\"#ff7a00\" stroke=\"none\"></circle><circle cx=\"14\" cy=\"12\" r=\"1\" fill=\"#ff7a00\" stroke=\"none\"></circle><line x1=\"11\" y1=\"11\" x2=\"11.5\" y2=\"11.5\" stroke=\"#ff7a00\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"></line><line x1=\"13\" y1=\"11\" x2=\"12.5\" y2=\"11.5\" stroke=\"#ff7a00\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"></line></svg><span>GamepadTester</span></a><div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-1\"><a class=\"px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-200 text-foreground-secondary hover:text-foreground hover:bg-surface-hover\" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-200 text-foreground-secondary hover:text-foreground hover:bg-surface-hover\" href=\"/calibration\">Calibration</a><a class=\"px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-200 text-foreground-secondary hover:text-foreground hover:bg-surface-hover\" href=\"/troubleshooting\">Help</a><a class=\"px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-200 text-foreground-secondary hover:text-foreground hover:bg-surface-hover\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a><a class=\"px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-200 text-foreground-secondary hover:text-foreground hover:bg-surface-hover\" href=\"/about\">About</a><button class=\"ml-3 p-2 rounded-lg bg-surface hover:bg-surface-hover border border-border transition-all duration-200\" aria-label=\"Toggle theme\" title=\"Switch to dark mode\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M21 12.79A9 9 0 1 1 11.21 3 7 7 0 0 0 21 12.79z\"></path></svg></button></div><div class=\"md:hidden flex items-center gap-2\"><button class=\"p-2 rounded-lg bg-surface border border-border\" aria-label=\"Toggle theme\">🌙</button><button class=\"p-2 rounded-lg bg-surface border border-border\" aria-label=\"Menu\"><svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></nav><div class=\"container-custom py-12 flex-1 max-w-4xl\"><div class=\"space-y-8\"><div><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 bg-success/15 border border-success/35 rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold text-success uppercase tracking-widest\">Security &amp; Privacy</span><h1 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black text-foreground tracking-tight mt-4\">Privacy Policy</h1><p class=\"text-foreground-muted text-xs sm:text-sm mt-2\">Last Updated: June 6, 2026</p></div><div class=\"bg-surface/50 border border-border rounded-3xl p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-xl backdrop-blur-md space-y-6 text-foreground-secondary leading-relaxed text-xs sm:text-sm\"><div class=\"space-y-3\"><h2 class=\"text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-foreground\">1. Zero Server Telemetry</h2><p>GamepadTester.live operates entirely on the client side. When you connect a PS5, PS4, Xbox, or Nintendo Switch controller, all inputs, button clicks, trigger values, and axis coordinates are processed inside your browser using the local Web Gamepad API.</p><p class=\"font-semibold text-primary\">Absolutely no telemetry data is transmitted to, stored on, or processed by our servers.</p></div><hr class=\"border-border/60\"/><div class=\"space-y-3\"><h2 class=\"text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-foreground\">2. No Account Registration</h2><p>You are never required to sign up, log in, or provide any personal details to use our testing dashboard. There are no profiles, credentials, or databases storing user information.</p></div><hr class=\"border-border/60\"/><div class=\"space-y-3\"><h2 class=\"text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-foreground\">3. Local Storage Preferences</h2><p>Our application uses your browser&#x27;s local storage solely to store interface configurations, such as your dark/light theme preference. This data never leaves your device and can be cleared at any time by emptying your browser cache.</p></div><hr class=\"border-border/60\"/><div class=\"space-y-3\"><h2 class=\"text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-foreground\">4. External Links</h2><p>Our blog sections and expert profiles contain links to outer channels, such as email addresses (`@gamepadtester.live`) and third-party developer documentation. We do not control and are not responsible for the privacy practices of external sites.</p></div><hr class=\"border-border/60\"/><div class=\"space-y-3\"><h2 class=\"text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-foreground\">5. Contacting Us</h2><p>If you have any questions regarding this policy or the technical execution of the Web Gamepad API on our site, feel free to contact our technical team at:</p><div class=\"bg-background/40 border border-border rounded-xl p-4 font-mono text-[11px] text-foreground-secondary\">Email: support@gamepadtester.live</div></div></div></div></div><footer class=\"bg-surface border-t border-border py-12\"><div class=\"container-custom\"><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-8\"><div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold gradient-text mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><svg class=\"inline-block\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#ff7a00\" stroke-width=\"2.2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle\"><rect x=\"2\" y=\"6\" width=\"20\" height=\"12\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"rgba(255, 122, 0, 0.12)\"></rect><path d=\"M6 12h4M8 10v4\" stroke=\"#ff7a00\" stroke-width=\"2.2\"></path><circle cx=\"16\" cy=\"10\" r=\"1\" fill=\"#ff7a00\" stroke=\"none\"></circle><circle cx=\"18\" cy=\"12\" r=\"1\" fill=\"#ff7a00\" stroke=\"none\"></circle><circle cx=\"16\" cy=\"14\" r=\"1\" fill=\"#ff7a00\" stroke=\"none\"></circle><circle cx=\"14\" cy=\"12\" r=\"1\" fill=\"#ff7a00\" stroke=\"none\"></circle><line x1=\"11\" y1=\"11\" x2=\"11.5\" y2=\"11.5\" stroke=\"#ff7a00\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"></line><line x1=\"13\" y1=\"11\" x2=\"12.5\" y2=\"11.5\" stroke=\"#ff7a00\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"></line></svg> GamepadTester</h3><p class=\"text-foreground-muted text-sm\">Professional gamepad testing platform with advanced diagnostics.</p></div><div><h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-4\">Quick Links</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-foreground-muted\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-accent transition\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-accent transition\" href=\"/calibration\">Calibration</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-accent transition\" href=\"/blog\">Blog &amp; Guides</a></li></ul></div><div><h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-4\">Resources</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-foreground-muted\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-accent transition\" href=\"/troubleshooting\">Troubleshooting</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-accent transition\" href=\"/about\">About Us</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-accent transition\" href=\"/privacy\">Privacy Policy</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-accent transition\" href=\"/terms\">Terms of Use</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-accent transition\" href=\"/contact\">Contact Us</a></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"border-t border-border pt-8 flex justify-between items-center text-sm text-foreground-muted\"><p>© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> GamepadTester.live. All rights reserved.</p><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><a class=\"hover:text-accent transition\" href=\"/privacy\">Privacy</a><a class=\"hover:text-accent transition\" href=\"/terms\">Terms</a></div></div></div></footer></main><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-48b11d9153e4dd91.js\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0]);self.__next_f.push([2,null])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:HL[\\\"/_next/static/css/ed9a2c062f73b56c.css\\\",\\\"style\\\"]\\n2:HL[\\\"/_next/static/css/c33ec7901e0fca6e.css\\\",\\\"style\\\"]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"3:I[2846,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n5:I[1344,[\\\"448\\\",\\\"static/chunks/448-b3255ce07fb7af32.js\\\",\\\"54\\\",\\\"static/chunks/54-2c8bd0f3e065c835.js\\\",\\\"385\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/privacy/page-5893913c1824f60f.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n6:I[8349,[\\\"448\\\",\\\"static/chunks/448-b3255ce07fb7af32.js\\\",\\\"54\\\",\\\"static/chunks/54-2c8bd0f3e065c835.js\\\",\\\"385\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/privacy/page-5893913c1824f60f.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n7:I[4707,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n8:I[6423,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n9:I[8003,[\\\"185\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/layout-a6e49f9b6a696646.js\\\"],\\\"\\\"]\\nb:I[1060,[],\\\"\\\"]\\nc:[]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"0:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L3\\\",null,{\\\"buildId\\\":\\\"D7407cpxK30cjVt1hKs9V\\\",\\\"assetPrefix\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlParts\\\":[\\\"\\\",\\\"privacy\\\"],\\\"initialTree\\\":[\\\"\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"privacy\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"__PAGE__\\\",{}]}]},\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"$undefined\\\",true],\\\"initialSeedData\\\":[\\\"\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"privacy\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"__PAGE__\\\",{},[[\\\"$L4\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"main\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"min-h-screen bg-background flex flex-col 