tracking-widest\",\"children\":\"Security & Privacy\"}],[\"$\",\"h1\",null,{\"className\":\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black text-foreground tracking-tight mt-4\",\"children\":\"Privacy Policy\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-foreground-muted text-xs sm:text-sm mt-2\",\"children\":\"Last Updated: June 6, 2026\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"bg-surface/50 border border-border rounded-3xl p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-xl backdrop-blur-md space-y-6 text-foreground-secondary leading-relaxed text-xs sm:text-sm\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-foreground\",\"children\":\"1. Zero Server Telemetry\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"GamepadTester.live operates entirely on the client side. When you connect a PS5, PS4, Xbox, or Nintendo Switch controller, all inputs, button clicks, trigger values, and axis coordinates are processed inside your browser using the local Web Gamepad API.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-primary\",\"children\":\"Absolutely no telemetry data is transmitted to, stored on, or processed by our servers.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"hr\",null,{\"className\":\"border-border/60\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-foreground\",\"children\":\"2. No Account Registration\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"You are never required to sign up, log in, or provide any personal details to use our testing dashboard. There are no profiles, credentials, or databases storing user information.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"hr\",null,{\"className\":\"border-border/60\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-foreground\",\"children\":\"3. Local Storage Preferences\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Our application uses your browser's local storage solely to store interface configurations, such as your dark/light theme preference. This data never leaves your device and can be cleared at any time by emptying your browser cache.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"hr\",null,{\"className\":\"border-border/60\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-foreground\",\"children\":\"4. External Links\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Our blog sections and expert profiles contain links to outer channels, such as email addresses (`@gamepadtester.live`) and third-party developer documentation. We do not control and are not responsible for the privacy practices of external sites.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"hr\",null,{\"className\":\"border-border/60\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-foreground\",\"children\":\"5. Contacting Us\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"If you have any questions regarding this policy or the technical execution of the Web Gamepad API on our site, feel free to contact our technical team at:\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"bg-background/40 border border-border rounded-xl p-4 font-mono text-[11px] text-foreground-secondary\",\"children\":\"Email: support@gamepadtester.live\"}]]}]]}]]}]}],[\"$\",\"$L3\",null,{}]]}],null],null],null]},[null,[\"$\",\"$L4\",null,{\"parallelRouterKey\":\"children\",\"segmentPath\":[\"children\",\"privacy\",\"children\"],\"error\":\"$undefined\",\"errorStyles\":\"$undefined\",\"errorScripts\":\"$undefined\",\"template\":[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{}],\"templateStyles\":\"$undefined\",\"templateScripts\":\"$undefined\",\"notFound\":\"$undefined\",\"notFoundStyles\":\"$undefined\"}]],null]},[[[[\"$\",\"link\",\"0\",{\"rel\":\"stylesheet\",\"href\":\"/_next/static/css/ed9a2c062f73b56c.css\",\"precedence\":\"next\",\"crossOrigin\":\"$undefined\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"1\",{\"rel\":\"stylesheet\",\"hre